# Work Tab Mobile UI - Prototype & Visual Specifications

## Overview
This document presents the complete UI prototype for the Work tab, following iOS 26 design standards and maintaining consistency with the existing dashboard UI.

---

## Generated Mockups

### 1. Work Dashboard Landing Page

![Work Dashboard Landing](C:/Users/Admin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/eb17ffba-1a04-4a56-9be7-876c09814b38/work_dashboard_landing_1768366720498.png)

**Key Features**:
- Clean header with back navigation and user avatar
- Three summary cards for quick access to Tasks, Meetings, and Calendar
- Each card shows preview data (task count, upcoming meetings, events)
- Floating action button for quick creation
- Follows inset grouped list pattern from dashboard

---

### 2. My Tasks View

![My Tasks View](C:/Users/Admin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/eb17ffba-1a04-4a56-9be7-876c09814b38/work_tasks_view_1768366746242.png)

**Key Features**:
- Segmented control to switch between "My Tasks" and "By Project"
- Quick filter pills (Today, This Week, All)
- Tasks grouped by status (TODO, DOING, DONE)
- Priority indicators (colored dots)
- Metadata icons (comments, attachments, subtasks)
- Clean card-based layout

