## Interaction Patterns

### Navigation
- **Tap Card**: Navigate to detail view
- **Swipe Left**: Reveal quick actions (delete, edit)
- **Pull to Refresh**: Update data
- **Swipe Down**: Dismiss modal

### Quick Actions
- **Long Press FAB**: Show quick action preview
- **Tap FAB**: Open action sheet
- **Tap Filter Pill**: Toggle filter
- **Tap Segmented Control**: Switch view

### Gestures
- **Horizontal Swipe** (Calendar): Change day/week
- **Vertical Scroll**: Browse content
- **Pinch** (Calendar Day View): Zoom time scale

