## Accessibility Features

### VoiceOver Labels
- All interactive elements have descriptive labels
- Card content is grouped for efficient navigation
- Status changes are announced

### Dynamic Type
- All text scales with system font size settings
- Layouts adapt to larger text sizes
- Minimum touch targets maintained

### Color Contrast
- All text meets WCAG AA standards (4.5:1 for body, 3:1 for large text)
- Icons have sufficient contrast
- Focus indicators are visible

### Haptic Feedback
- Button taps: Light impact
- Successful actions: Success notification
- Errors: Error notification
- Swipe actions: Selection feedback

