## Responsive Behavior

### iPhone SE (Small Screen)
- Single column layout
- Compact spacing (reduce to 12px margins)
- Smaller font sizes (scale down 1-2pt)
- Horizontal scroll for filter pills

### iPhone Pro Max (Large Screen)
- Standard layout
- Full spacing (16px margins)
- Standard font sizes
- More content visible

### iPad
- Two-column layout for dashboard
- Master-detail split view for task/meeting details
- Wider cards (max 600px)
- Side-by-side modals

